12 BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES AND THE SENATE OF THE
13 2ND SESSION OF THE 60TH OKLAHOMA LEGISLATURE:
14 SECTION 1. The Secretary of State shall refer to the people for
15 their approval or rejection, as and in the manner provided by law,
16 the following proposed amendment to Section 8C of Article X of the
17 Constitution of the State of Oklahoma to read as follows:
18 Section 8C. A. Despite any provision to the contrary,
19 beginning January 1, 2005 2027, the fair cash value, as determined
20 by law, on each homestead of an individual head of household whose
21 gross household income from all sources for the preceding calendar
22 year did not exceed an amount as provided in subsection B of this
23 section, and which individual head of household who is sixty-five
24 (65) years of age or older who has occupied the property for a
