1 prop erty, the total fair cash value shall not exceed the revised
2 valuation of the property so long as the individual head of
3 household who is sixty-five (65) years of age or older owns and
4 occupies the property and so long as the gross household income from
5 all sources does not exceed an amount as provided in subsection B of
